{"tid":349074,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC][Steam]世紀帝國 Age of Empires II HD (2)","createTime":"2017-08-06T09:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T02:44:19.000Z","uid":34955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a66d5ce5093d594edc8150d2400982847771702e","tid":349074,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.game4v.com/2016/06/maxresdefault-15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.game4v.com%2F2016%2F06%2Fmaxresdefault-15.jpg&h=ae9857eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/17d7d0e76bbd74165101b6175995003f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net%2F17d7d0e76bbd74165101b6175995003f.jpg&h=dc5fab5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經典不解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱個更新終於解決埋連線問題<br />\n基本上依家搵世界各國嘅人開拖都唔會lag得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSteam link:<br />\n<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/221380/Age_of_Empires_II_HD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F221380%2FAge_of_Empires_II_HD%2F&d=%2FMMeF6UuYojV3BWlM6jOVAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=724daae3\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/221380/Age_of_Empires_II_HD/</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3976137d00dbb7e405f18d2f0fa30ff2683d2de","tid":349074,"uid":34955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:23:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">繁體中文化：</span></span><br />\n　　１、請將遊戲語言轉換至簡體中文（收藏庫&gt;AOE II&gt;右鍵&gt;內容&gt;語言）；<br />\n　　２、請訂閱繁體中文化插件：<a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=466768643\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsteamcommunity.com%2Fsharedfiles%2Ffiledetails%2F%3Fid%3D466768643&d=%2FMMeF6UuYojV3BWlM6jOVAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=71b40f11\" target=\"_blank\">http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=466768643</a>；<br />\n　　３、進入遊戲，原則上就是繁體中文。若不是，請在遊戲中的「選項」中選擇「繁體中文」。<br />\n　　【到這步就可以算是繁化成功了。不過只有遊戲內文。】<br />\n<br />\n※ 請注意：由於工作坊本身的問題，雖然可以簡單轉換繁體、自動更新最新文本內容，但啟動器卻無法自動置換，因此若想達到完美繁化，請續行老步驟：<br />\n<br />\n　　４、訂閱之後，Steam 會自動幫您下載檔案（參看底部下載列），完成後，<br />\n　　至X:\\Steam\\steamapps\\workshop\\content\\221380\\466768643 內，<br />\n　　將所有檔案覆蓋進 X:\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\Age2HD。<br />\n　　（此處的X，是您安裝Steam的位置，可能是D槽也可能是C槽）<br />\n　　５、最後，進入遊戲就完美繁化了！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">資料來源：<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=01122&amp;snA=12498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D01122%26snA%3D12498&d=%2FMMeF6UuYojV3BWlM6jOVAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=8c7449f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=01122&amp;snA=12498</a></span>"},{"pid":"a6c9bb91317550e3783b71cfde85df5ed41b338d","tid":349074,"uid":34955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:25:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">舊post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/81759\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/81759</a></span>"},{"pid":"3fa6ffa2e7a6265ed648829a05571c5902824ca0","tid":349074,"uid":76380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:27:53.000Z","msg":"而家重有得 / 人玩？ 真經典"},{"pid":"9805ca7be203587a3091e9d6839fda771d32f466","tid":349074,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:48:18.000Z","msg":"個mouse 玩正版唔係玩得好順 老翻就無問題<br />\n點搞"},{"pid":"28b00b5a47234ea901f668c0db6dd22faf6c000d","tid":349074,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:31:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家重有得 / 人玩？ 真經典</blockquote><br />\nOK多架<br />\n晚晚都見到有人開中文名嘅房<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm