citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:00:41.000Z","msg":"人口一多就lag問題幾時解決<br />\n而家玩cba仍然有d唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c689be50834fb5961cb56abc12a7ebdc3141f3ce","tid":349074,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人口一多就lag問題幾時解決<br />\n而家玩cba仍然有d唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇咁快架啦<br />\n係佢未更新之前唯有記住每場最多1600人呢個上限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒就上吓官方forum鞭策下佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfeafdd6505278b0783daa0a7d462234945127da","tid":349074,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T13:11:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">啱啱出左更新</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPatch 5.5 has now cleared Open Beta and been promoted to Live! <br />\n<br />\nThank you to everyone who participated in this long Open Beta and we are thrilled to bring these desync improvements and balance changes to the full community! As always, your feedback has been valuable and your assistance playing multiplayer games has ensured that our desync rates have improved.<br />\n<br />\nThe new discussion thread can be found here and we look forward to hearing from you and collecting your feedback!<br />\n<br />\nStability and Performance Improvements:<br />\nPerformance optimizations should increase frame rates up to 15%<br />\nResearching spies during treaty should no longer causes a desync<br />\nExtremely long games should no longer desync due to high turn counts<br />\nQuitting via ALT+F4 should no longer cause a desync<br />\nResigning but staying in game no longer desyncs after remaining players save/load<br />\nThe desync message should no longer appear over the post game screen<br />\n<br />\nCommunity Focused Bug Fixes:<br />\nHosts are able to set a password for their lobby<br />\nAudio for notifications should no longer overlap and cause a loud noise<br />\nAudio for garrisoning / un-garrisoning should no longer overlap<br />\nLobby civ pools should now be consistent for each host player<br />\nLobby civ pools should now display the conquerors civilizations correctly<br />\nLobby maps should now display random special and real world at the top of the list<br />\nLobby maps no longer displays random special twice in the list<br />\nLobby maps now select DLC3 Random Real World maps correctly when appropriate<br />\nThe password checkbox should now remain when changing datasets<br />\nNavigating through <a href=\"http://aoe.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Faoe.net&d=%2FMMeF6UuYojV3BWlM6jOVAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=75a16185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">aoe.net</a> should now correctly prompt the password popup (when needed)<br />\n<br />\nBalance Improvements:<br />\nMagyars no longer need to build a blacksmith to receive free blacksmith upgrades<br />\nMagyars now receive Siege Engineers<br />\nMagyar Scout Cavalry, Light Cavalry and Hussar cost -15% (up from -10%)<br />\nMagyars Recurve Bow now adds +1 attack and +1 range (up from +1 range)<br />\nIndians no longer have the Arbalest upgrade<br />\nMalay Karambit Warrior have +1 attack<br />\nFire ships have -1 pierce armor<br />\nFast Fire ships have -1 pierce armor<br />\nViking warship discount changed to -15%, -15%, -20% (up from -10%, -15%, -20%)<br />\nItalians fishing ships now cost -15 wood (down from -25 wood)"},{"pid":"693d28d7c0a85035629b06e658739fd3533db7a7","tid":349074,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T13:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>AOE4確認<br />\n唔知會唔會係手機game呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/368850/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/368850/</a></blockquote><br />\nbtw,  確認咗喺windows 10 only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffc9b6d9d7d34c1bc53d16e7281c5baa42312a8","tid":349074,"uid":4846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T18:31:47.000Z","msg":"成日比電腦屌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07276b7529f88ef51297b4d2907776a6177744d","tid":349074,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:16:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日比電腦屌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新手可以試下封建時代開始狂起城牆/「屋牆」<br />\n利用ai死都要清哂眼前嘅野呢個弱點俾時間自已海兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898a739886d30dafc25e855333d29b833c61ef18","tid":349074,"uid":18333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果aoc唔係20年前出嘅話<br />\n白日夢可能已經發左達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347963/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347963/</a></blockquote><br />\nRTS 就算依家出都唔會發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8894f07f14c7fd06d2655899b6f05266f0284d46","tid":349074,"uid":44789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"係咪淨係買$119 就可以玩晒所有文明?<br />\n幾時會有特價"},{"pid":"4644050cf5efef9e5d95c0e0825680d818c534cf","tid":349074,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪淨係買$119 就可以玩晒所有文明?<br />\n幾時會有特價</blockquote><br />\n$119會有哂當年AOE果啲文明<br />\n其他AOFE/新文明就要買DLC<br />\n<br />\n至於特價方面一般steam有就會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c282ebcf05146f7247e387df15ceca48f8d064","tid":349074,"uid":50320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:31:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪淨係買$119 